{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"baffdc2ec4","title":"攻占眠州战略上十分有利","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b280d08d62","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":13,"articleId":"baffdc2ec4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6390e35030","type":"paragraph","text":"攻占眠州战略上十分有利","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"6cb33ad17c","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月13日）朱、张、任同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"d06932e687","type":"paragraph","text":"如能攻占眠州城，则打马打毛打王均十分有利，战略上大占优胜。万一攻不开，则围城打援。毛炳文现正以一部从陇西增援，是消灭他的好机会。朱总司令宜速派人去见王均曾万钟，彼等孤危，不难收效。城内鲁大昌亦宜派人，允许放他向临潭跑。如何，望的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"99c2bd3da1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛周彭","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"d2bf70daa5","type":"paragraph","text":"十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"66e5131283","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和周恩来，西北革命军事委员会副主席、红军第一方面军司令员彭德怀给朱德和红军总政治委员张国春、红军第二方面军政治委员任强时的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"19145ab3a5","type":"paragraph","text":"121眠州，即甘肃眠县。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"9b3af80566","type":"paragraph","text":"[31马，指马步芳，当时任国民党青海省政府代主席、国民党军西北“”总司令部新编第二军军长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"c87f04345a","type":"paragraph","text":"141毛，指毛炳文，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第三十七军军长。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"},{"id":"6072f08fbe","type":"paragraph","text":"王，指王均，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第三军军长。[6]曾万钟，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第三军第七师师长。[7]鲁大昌，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部新编第十四师师长。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4"}],"page":{"id":"425200ea38","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"baffdc2ec4","start":64,"end":64}}}},"__N_SSG":true}